{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/paperfaces/grantlandram-portrait/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Grayscale and Pencil and Blend oh my!","date":"2013-12-09T00:00:00.000Z","date_pretty":"December 9th, 2013","date_from_now":"7 years ago","last_modified_at":null,"last_modified_at_from_now":null,"path":"/paperfaces/grantlandram-portrait/","author":null,"excerpt":"PaperFaces portrait of @GrantLandram drawn with Paper for iOS on an iPad.","tags":["portrait","illustration","Paper for iOS","black and white","time lapse"],"image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"aspectRatio":1.3349514563106797,"src":"/static/f921115f9e34798312976ed9f75c8640/fc20c/paperfaces-grantlandram-twitter.jpg","srcSet":"/static/f921115f9e34798312976ed9f75c8640/6e883/paperfaces-grantlandram-twitter.jpg 275w,\n/static/f921115f9e34798312976ed9f75c8640/a09ef/paperfaces-grantlandram-twitter.jpg 550w,\n/static/f921115f9e34798312976ed9f75c8640/fc20c/paperfaces-grantlandram-twitter.jpg 1100w,\n/static/f921115f9e34798312976ed9f75c8640/5d6ff/paperfaces-grantlandram-twitter.jpg 1650w,\n/static/f921115f9e34798312976ed9f75c8640/d2f4e/paperfaces-grantlandram-twitter.jpg 2048w","sizes":"(max-width: 1100px) 100vw, 1100px"},"fixed":{"src":"/static/f921115f9e34798312976ed9f75c8640/fc20c/paperfaces-grantlandram-twitter.jpg","height":825,"width":1100}}},"toc":null,"comments":null,"comments_locked":null,"hide_meta":null},"id":"a3cf0a75-79bd-54bd-bdc1-52f22ea3a52b","html":"<p>PaperFaces portrait of <a href=\"https://twitter.com/GrantLandram\">@GrantLandram</a>.</p>\n<p>Decided to try and create a true time lapse video showing off 53’s new Pencil stylus another go. </p>\n<p>To record the footage I used a <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B007NFI656/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&#x26;camp=1789&#x26;creative=390957&#x26;creativeASIN=B007NFI656&#x26;linkCode=as2&#x26;tag=mademist-20\">cheap GorillaPod knockoff</a> to mount my iPhone 5s around a floor lamp. Once attached I swung it over my desk to get a top down view of the iPad’s screen. To record I used the iOS app <a href=\"http://www.lapseit.com/\"><strong>Lapse It</strong></a> to capture an image every second and then output as a 1080p MP4 video that could be edited further in <strong>Adobe After Effects</strong>.</p>\n<p>The time lapse effect came out ok, but have to look at lighting the work area better next time. Most of the footage was way too dark and the whites on the iPad’s screen super blown out, which made setting an accurate white balance challenging.</p>\n<p><div class=\"gatsby-resp-iframe-wrapper\" style=\"padding-bottom: 56.42857142857143%; position: relative; height: 0; overflow: hidden; \" > <div class=\"embedVideo-container\"> <iframe data-src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/JqVzqVG0e5g?rel=0\" class=\"embedVideo-iframe lazyload\" style=\"border:0; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; \" allowfullscreen></iframe> </div> </div></p>\n<p><strong>Tools used:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://amzn.to/35tCkJW\">Pencil by FiftyThree</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://paper.bywetransfer.com/\">Paper for iOS</a></li>\n</ul>","excerpt":"PaperFaces portrait of @GrantLandram. Decided to try and create a true time lapse video showing off 53’s new Pencil stylus another go.  To…","timeToRead":1,"tableOfContents":""},"comments":{"edges":[]}},"pageContext":{"next":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/paperfaces/esty-c-portrait/","title":"For the flowers against pink","categories":["paperfaces"],"tags":["portrait","illustration","Paper for iOS","Sktchy","time lapse"]},"fileAbsolutePath":"/home/28041/opensource/github.com/mmistakes/made-mistakes-gatsby/src/posts/paperfaces/esty-c-portrait.md"},"previous":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/paperfaces/effy-e-portrait/","title":"Undercut inspiration","categories":["paperfaces"],"tags":["portrait","illustration","Paper for iOS","Sktchy"]},"fileAbsolutePath":"/home/28041/opensource/github.com/mmistakes/made-mistakes-gatsby/src/posts/paperfaces/effy-e-portrait.md"}}}}